de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.tnccs.im.loader

Interface ImLoader<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the loadable type (e.g. IMC or IMV)
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultImLoader

    public interface ImLoader<T>
    Generic loader to load IM(C/V) according to a configuration entry and handle the class path for the IM(C/V).

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void cleanUp(Set<ConfigurationEntry> currentConfigs)
      Enables the loader to check the currently valid configuration entries to adapt its internal class paths to the current configuration entries.

      Loads an IM(C/V) according to the given configuration entry.
      List<T> loadIms(List<ConfigurationEntry> configs)
      Loads a list of IM(C/V) according to the given configuration entries.
